                <h1>Walk the Iconic Abbey Road Crosswalk: A Tribute to The Beatles</h1>
                <p>The Abbey Road crosswalk, made famous by The Beatles' iconic album cover, attracts tourists and fans worldwide. Located near Abbey Road Studios in London, this pedestrian zebra crossing symbolizes music history. Visitors often reenact the famous photo, capturing the moment with their own camera shots, making it a must-see landmark.</p>
